How to compile the code:
make

How to execute the code:
0 - small processing type
1 - large processing type

./unified 0 ../../shakespeare.txt
./unified 1 ../../wikipedia.txt

To get the same (or approximated) files in the results folder do it:
./timediff 5 './unified 0 ../../shakespeare.txt' > time_serial_small.txt
./timediff 5 './unified 1 ../../wikipedia.txt' > time_serial_large.txt

./unified 0 ../../shakespeare.txt > saida_serial_small.txt
./unified 1 ../../wikipedia.txt > saida_serial_large.txt
